channel.title: Telugu character how does it works?
channel.description: #Telugu Hi, so I think all in here are aware of the telugu char, the one that crashes apple devices. Most of my friends own Iphone and they have received this character, and they've come to me for a solution. I have spend 1 complete day answering my friend's cry for help, between all this helping I wonder, how can a character crash a phone almost at the point when it doesn't turns on?
